==English==

===Adjective===
'''parentage'''

# Of or pertaining to one's parents, and in particular, the [[legitimacy]] of one's birth.
 
# The social quality of your class in society. 
#:'''1608''' ''My fortunes -- parentage -- good parentage -- To equal mine! -- was it not thus? What say you?''  Shakespeare, ''Pericles'', Act 5, Scene 1.

